<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/655975-andr">André</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The whole book has 148 pages, but the main part is only 100 pages. This is followed by an appendix and notes on the following 31 pages. Then two pages<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The whole book has 148 pages, but the main part is only 100 pages. This is followed by an appendix and notes on the following 31 pages. Then two pages of references and 13 pages of closing remarks not by the author himself.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
